ğŸ”¸ **B-1. Server Restarts**:| 
|Upon the 5-minute mark before a restart, the following guidelines apply:|
|
â¤ No initiating new hunts/contests are prohibited.|
â¤ Abstain from new engagements or provocations.|
â¤ Ongoing actions from before the announcement may continue.|
â¤ Pre-existing engagements shall not be interrupted; no interference from any species is allowed.|
|
|
|
ğŸ”¸ **B-2. Fair Play**:|  
|â¤ Specifically targeting or seeking revenge on players is not permitted. Avoid behaviors that feel personal or vindictive.|
|
|
|
ğŸ”¸ **B-3. Respectful Hunting**:|  
|â¤ Hunting purely for sport (KFS) is frowned upon. For instance, killing on sight and not consuming the prey.|
|
|
|
ğŸ”¸ **B-4. Game Integrity**:|  
|Avoid behaviors that compromise the game's spirit:|
|
â¤ No dino swapping for scouting or claiming your own remains.|
â¤ Stay afloat in water only if stamina allows.|
â¤ Never disclose your or other's in-game locations in Global/Local.|
