ğŸ”¸ **B-5. Meshing**:|  
|Engage fairly without exploiting game meshes:|
|
â¤ Keep your dino's main body visible.|
â¤ Avoid glitching into terrains or obstacles.|
â¤ Attacking through obstructions is a no-go.|
|
|
|
ğŸ”¸ **B-6. Exploits & Loopholes**:|  
|â¤ Don't manipulate game loopholes or showcase them. Report any findings. For instance, manipulating spawns or the game environment isn't allowed.|
|
