|
ğŸ”¸ **B-7. Friendly Interaction Rules**:|  
|â¤ Following the use of a 2-call, there's a 15-minute hunting suspension. A mutual 2/4 call reinforces this. The use of a 3 call allows self-defense once reciprocated.|
|
|
|
ğŸ”¸ **B-8. Careful Assistance**:|  
|Avoid over-assisting:|
|
â¤ Avoid leading, feeding, or giving items to ungrouped dinos.|
